Encinitas.; Photo, Clockwise from above, he prepares to change reels during the 
nerve-wracking Switch-Over;; Photo, sorts through tickets in the kiosk before 
show time,; Photo, and hooks letters on the marquee outside. DON BARTLETTI / 
Los Angeles Times 
</P>
</GRAPHIC>
