UNITED STATES -- LABOR; PRODUCTIVITY; MEDICAL COSTS; UNITED STATES -- 
TRANSPORTATION; TOBACCO INDUSTRY; DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH AND HUMAN SERVICES 
(U.S.); SULLIVAN, LOUIS W 
</P>
