REDEVELOPMENT; INFRASTRUCTURE; PUERTO RICO -- EDUCATION; PUERTO RICO -- 
SCHOOLS; EDUCATION REFORM; HERNANDEZ COLON, RAFAEL; TELEPHONE INDUSTRY -- 
PUERTO RICO 
</P>
