DEFICIENCY SYNDROME; HUMAN IMMUNO DEFICIENCY VIRUS; NASCAR; SUITS; DOCTORS; 
LYING; TENNANT, FOREST; RICHMOND, TIM 
</P>
</SUBJECT>
