his gear. Squid have prospered in the sea, which is also known for marlin, 
pango, dorado and wahoos. ; Photo, Guide Marcello Geraldo lifts a large squid 
as partner Mario Coppola helps steady the boat. ; Photo, COLOR, FISHING: 
Roosterfish (pictured) is just one of many species to be found off La Paz, 
Mexico, in the Sea of Cortez. GARY FRIEDMAN / Los Angeles Times 
</P>
