for a shot at the huge jackpot.; Photo, Above, Cheryl Lee of Irvine hands over 
$135 to cashier for her tickets. She and co-workers pooled their money for the 
pot, which may top the record of $61.98 million. HENRY DIROCCO / For The Times; 
Photo, FOCUS Cheryl Lee of Irvine pooled her money with co-workers to buy Lotto 
tickets for tonight's huge jackpot. 
</P>
